Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,, Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,, And he later claimed she was burning up skin scorching hot even through his armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,, This is disturbing something inside her,\N something moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,, And the King's immediate reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,, Silence,\N Luka more instantly commanded him never to speak of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,, That's fast and telling why the secrecy,\N what was so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,, Well,\N the official account from grandmaster benefit is very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,, But septin barth's private journal,\N that tells a different story,\N a truly horrifying one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,, What did Barth write?
