Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,, And even Blarion,\N the black tread came back wounded,\N a massive nine foot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,, gash down his side bleeding smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,, So whatever area encountered,\N Valeria faced something awful too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,, It seems so,\N which makes Barth's comment certain doors are best left unopened,\N feel
